---
// TerminalIntro.astro
---

<div class="terminal">
  <div class="terminal-header">
    <span class="terminal-button red"></span>
    <span class="terminal-button yellow"></span>
    <span class="terminal-button green"></span>
    <span class="terminal-title">portfolio.sh</span>
  </div>
  <div class="terminal-body">
    <pre><code>$ ./portfolio.sh --info

Welcome to <strong>Crow's Portfolio</strong>

<span class="green">Name:</span> Crow
<span class="green">Role:</span> Software Engineer
<span class="green">Bio:</span> Passionate developer with experience in DevOps, Kubernetes, and web technologies.
         Always learning and building cool stuff.

 <span class="blue">Available Pages:</span>
   - <a href="/">Home</a>: Overview and navigation
   - <a href="/experience">Experience</a>: Professional background
   - <a href="/projects">Projects</a>: Featured work and projects
   - <a href="/certifications">Certifications</a>: Credentials and achievements

<span class="yellow">Theme:</span> Toggle between light and dark modes using the button in the header.

<span class="red">Contact:</span> Feel free to reach out for collaborations or questions!

$ <span class="cursor">_</span></span></code></pre>
  </div>
</div>



<style>
   .terminal {
     max-width: 100%;
     margin: 2rem auto;
     background: var(--bg);
     border: 1px solid var(--border);
     border-radius: 8px;
     font-family: 'Iosevka', monospace;
     box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
   }

  .terminal-header {
    background: var(--bg-soft);
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
  }

  .terminal-button {
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    margin-right: 8px;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .red { background: #ff5f57; }
  .yellow { background: #ffbd2e; }
  .green { background: #28ca42; }

  .terminal-title {
    flex: 1;
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--fg);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .terminal-body {
    padding: 1rem;
    color: var(--fg);
  }

  .terminal-body pre {
    margin: 0;
    background: transparent;
    border: none;
    padding: 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    white-space: pre-wrap;
    word-break: break-word;
  }

  .terminal-body code {
    background: transparent;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .terminal-body strong {
    color: var(--yellow);
  }

  .terminal-body .green {
    color: var(--green);
  }

  .terminal-body .blue {
    color: var(--blue);
  }

  .terminal-body .yellow {
    color: var(--yellow);
  }

  .terminal-body .red {
    color: var(--red);
  }

  .terminal-body a {
    color: var(--aqua);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .terminal-body a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  [data-theme="light"] .terminal-body a {
    color: var(--blue);
  }

  .cursor {
    animation: blink 1s infinite;
  }

  @keyframes blink {
    0%, 50% { opacity: 1; }
    51%, 100% { opacity: 0; }
  }

  /* Responsive */


  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .terminal {
      margin: 1rem;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }

    .terminal-header {
      padding: 0.3rem 0.5rem;
    }

    .terminal-body {
      padding: 0.5rem;
    }

    .terminal-title {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }
  }
</style>
